<%@ page contentType="text/html;charset=UTF-8" %>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Câu hỏi thường gặp</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 20px;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
        }
        .faq-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #000;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .question {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #000;
        }
        .answer {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="faq-container">
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="question">1. How to place an order?</div>
            <div class="answer">You can visit our store page, select the desired product, then click the "Add to Cart" button and follow the instructions to complete the order process.</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="question">2. What is the delivery time?</div>
            <div class="answer">The usual delivery time is 3-5 working days for urban areas and 5-7 working days for suburban and rural areas.</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="question">3. How much is the shipping fee?</div>
            <div class="answer">Shipping fees will be calculated based on your delivery address. The specific fee will be displayed during the checkout process before you confirm your order.</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="question">4. Can I cancel or change my order?</div>
            <div class="answer">You can cancel or change your order before it is shipped. Please contact our customer service via email or phone for assistance.</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="question">5. Does the store have a return policy?</div>
            <div class="answer">We have a return policy within 7 days from the date of receipt. Products must be intact, unused, and accompanied by the purchase invoice. For more details, please check the "Return Policy" page.</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="question">6. What payment methods can I use?</div>
            <div class="answer">We accept payment methods such as credit cards, debit cards, bank transfers, and cash on delivery (COD).</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="question">7. How can I contact the store?</div>
            <div class="answer">You can contact us via email at support@shopgiay.com or call us directly at (012) 3456 789. We will respond as soon as possible.</div>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>
</html>
